channel.title: StormScape [v718] [Dedicated]
channel.description:
Hello, I am starting a new server called StormScape, it's based on client version 718. The server is open to the internet, to sign up sign in with the username and password you want to use.
We have fully working skills, and give first time players free gifts!
We are looking for players AND staff, we will be up 24/7, suggestions are always welcome too.
Our website is http://stormscape.tk/ to start playing just click download and download the appropriate version for your system, if you have any problems please feel free to contact me via PM.
